! version = 2.0

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  Admin CRM Operations — ADR-010
//
//  Triggers the RapidPro CRM ops flow via the AI Gateway.
//  Authorization is enforced at the FLOW level (has_group guard),
//  not at the RiveBot level. This is defense-in-depth:
//    1. RiveBot triggers the flow for anyone who types "ops menu"
//    2. The flow's first node checks has_group(Admins)
//    3. Non-admins get "🚫 Access denied." and the flow ends
//
//  The macro returns {{noreply}} so the catch-all flow suppresses
//  any AI Gateway response. The RapidPro flow takes over the
//  WhatsApp session entirely.
//
//  Loaded in _common/ so it works across ALL personas.
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

// ── CRM Ops Entry Points ─────────────────────────────────────

+ ops
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ ops menu
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ ops menu *
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ * ops menu
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ * ops menu *
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ admin ops
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ admin ops *
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ * admin ops
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ * admin ops *
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ crm
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

+ crm *
- <call>start_crm_ops</call>

// ── CRM Discovery Triggers (Layer A) ─────────────────────────────
// Matched BEFORE AI fallback when admin asks HOW to access operations.
// Sends a WuzAPI Quick Reply button with DisplayText="ops menu".
// When tapped, WhatsApp sends the literal text "ops menu" → RiveBot
// matches it above → fires start_crm_ops. Zero LLM involvement.

+ [*] how [*] crm [*]
- <call>send_crm_help</call>

+ [*] how [*] ops [*]
- <call>send_crm_help</call>

+ [*] admin [*] access [*]
- <call>send_crm_help</call>

+ [*] admin [*] menu [*]
- <call>send_crm_help</call>

+ [*] how [*] manage [*] contact [*]
- <call>send_crm_help</call>

+ [*] how [*] manage [*] workspace [*]
- <call>send_crm_help</call>

// ── Static Help Command (ADR-011 Finding 4) ──────────────────────
// Returns a hardcoded list of available commands. No LLM involved.
// Updated for Layer 2 direct commands.

+ help
- 📋 *Available Commands:*\n\n*Guided Mode:*\n🔹 *ops* — Open the CRM menu\n\n*Direct Commands:*\n🔹 *list groups* — List all segments\n🔹 *lookup \<phone\>* — Look up a contact\n🔹 *org info* — Show workspace info\n🔹 *create group \<name\>* — Create a segment\n🔹 *help* — Show this list\n\n💡 All commands require admin access.

+ help *
- {@ help}

// ── Layer 2 Direct Commands (ADR-011 T2) ─────────────────────────
// These bypass the flow system entirely. RiveBot → macro_bridge →
// Gateway tool → RapidPro API → formatted WhatsApp response.
// Auth is enforced in macro_bridge.py via _verify_admin().

+ list groups
- <call>crm_list_groups</call>

+ list segments
- <call>crm_list_groups</call>

+ lookup *
- <call>crm_lookup_contact <star></call>

+ org info
- <call>crm_org_info</call>

+ org
- <call>crm_org_info</call>

+ create group *
- <call>crm_create_group <star></call>

+ create segment *
- <call>crm_create_group <star></call>

// ── Near-Miss Error Patterns (ADR-011 Finding 6) ─────────────────
// Catch partial or incomplete commands BEFORE they fall through to
// the catch-all → Hermes. Provides actionable syntax hints.

+ broadcast to *
- ⚠️ Broadcast is a guided-only operation.\n\nType *ops* → Messages → Broadcast for safe broadcast with confirmation.

+ broadcast
- ⚠️ Broadcast is a guided-only operation.\n\nType *ops* → Messages → Broadcast for safe broadcast with confirmation.

+ lookup
- ⚠️ Missing phone number.\n\n*Usage:* `lookup <phone number>`

+ send to *
- ⚠️ Send is a guided-only operation.\n\nType *ops* → Messages → Send for safe message delivery.

+ send
- ⚠️ Missing recipient and message.\n\nType *ops* → Messages → Send for guided mode.

+ create group
- ⚠️ Missing segment name.\n\n*Usage:* `create group <name>`

+ create segment
- ⚠️ Missing segment name.\n\n*Usage:* `create segment <name>`

+ create
- ⚠️ Missing what to create.\n\n*Available:* `create group <name>`\n\n💡 Or type *ops* for the full menu.

+ delete group
- ⚠️ Segment deletion requires confirmation.\n\nType *ops* → Segments → Delete for guided mode with safety guard.

+ delete
- ⚠️ Deletion requires confirmation.\n\nType *ops* for the full CRM menu with safety guards.

+ list
- ⚠️ Missing what to list.\n\n*Available:* `list groups`\n\n💡 Or type *ops* for the full menu.
